{"groups":[{"groupKey":"120363407384623871@g.us","name":"120363407384623871@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":4,"lastActive":1784517548199,"messages":[{"sender":"Yu Gil","text":"Good morning Coze team😊\nQuick question, how do we dispose of cardboard materials?","ts":1784512274992},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Please place the cardboard materials next to the outdoor trash bins. Our team will take care of them. Thank you! 😊","ts":1784512536910},{"sender":"Yu Gil","text":"Ok thank you 😊","ts":1784512669730},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello 😊 @188584162275518 \n\nYour airport transportation for tomorrow’s 4:30 a.m. departure has been fully arranged, and the driver has already been assigned. The driver will also assist you with moving and loading your luggage into the vehicle.\n\nAs your departure is very early, we hope you can get some comfortable rest as early as possible this evening.\n\nPlease also note that the building is mostly residential, and the neighbors will still be sleeping at that time. We would greatly appreciate it if you could prepare and leave as quietly and carefully as possible. 🙏\n\nThank you so much for your understanding and kind cooperation.\n\nCyrus\nGuest Care Team of COZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1784517548199}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:301321483004194","name":"kakao:301321483004194","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":16,"lastActive":1784516788131,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_RICKY","text":"26년 7월 20일 금요일 13:40PM\n\n인천->HT\n\nMM705\n\n 藪 裕太朗\n\n성인6  / 점보1  / 11만원 / 후불","ts":1784492994642},{"sender":"COZE_RICKY","text":"26년 7월 20일 금요일 13:40PM\n\n인천->HT\n\nMM705\n\n 藪 裕太朗\n\n성인6  / 점보1  / 11만원 / 후불","ts":1784492995930},{"sender":"COZE_RICKY","text":"{\"logId\":3888587832588947457,\"targetRevision\":1,\"hidden\":true,\"feedType\":25}","ts":1784493148790},{"sender":"COZE_RICKY","text":"26년 7월 20일 금요일 13:40PM\n\n인천->HT\n\nMM705\n\n 藪裕太朗 (일본게스트)\n\n성인6  / 점보1  / 11만원 / 후불","ts":1784493149293},{"sender":"COZE_RICKY","text":"{\"logId\":388858